 (coffee website)
 user enter website http://wwww.sitandsip.com
 user opens web page. As soon as user opens webpage. User will see images of food and beverages items will be displayed on top half of screen. 
 A short summary of the owner and how the shop got started was displayed right below the images.
 At the top left corner show a hambuger icon for menu, prices and reservations.
 If user would like to check out menu image items.
 user will click menu and be able to see images.
 If user would like to check out prices. User would have to click for prices. A menu item list will be shown with price cost,
 Later if user decides to make reservation. user will click for reservation.
 user will taken to another page to be able to provide information.
 User will provide email address, phone number, and name. 
 Calendar will be shown where the user can click and be abke to choose a date and time. 
 after date is choossen. Different times will be displayed which user will choose from.
 After date and time is choosen a comfirmation will sent to the user. 
 information is sent via email or text.
 If the user decides to cancel or reschedule can do so via text by link in text. 
user leave web page http://wwww.sitandsip.com